Class DynamicColorDialog

  • java.lang.Object

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    android.arch.lifecycle.LifecycleOwner, android.arch.lifecycle.ViewModelStoreOwner, ComponentCallbacks, DialogInterface.OnCancelListener, DialogInterface.OnDismissListener, View.OnCreateContextMenuListener

    public class DynamicColorDialog
extends DynamicDialogFragment
    A color picker dialog fragment to display multiple grids of colors and their shades. It will be used internally by the DynamicColorPreference but can be used by the other views also.
